---
layout: default
title: SME Growth Hub
---

<section id="course-cta-header" class="fixed top-0 bg-white flex space-between mx-auto z-50 shadow py-2 lg:py-4 w-full">
  <div class="flex inner justify-between items-center">
    <div class="flex items-center">
      <div class="logo mr-8 hidden sm:block">
        <img class="block h-10 md:h-10 w-auto" src="../../../images/tcg-logo/Blue/The_Coders_Guild_Logo_Blue.svg" alt="The Coders Guild Logo">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row">
      {% include './includes/components/hub/consultation-button.njk' %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="bg-grey-100">
  <section class="relative flex flex-col bg-white gap-10">
    <div class="bg-blue-100/5 relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:gap-10 px-4 lg:px-48 pb-32">
      <div class="relative py-48 lg:order-2">
        <object class="absolute left-[-10rem] top-[5rem] pattern" data="../images/patterns/2.svg" type="image/svg+xml"></object>
        <div class="relative">
          <img src="../images/learner-images/learners-in-agile-software-development.jpeg" alt="Learners in agile software development" class="relative rounded shadow-lg" />
          <div class="absolute bottom-[-10%] left-[5%]">
            <script src="https://widget.trustist.com/JgTmKy9K3kqIxBnXqyliBg/trustistreviewer.js"></script>
            <div ts-widget="" ts-border-radius="15px" ts-suppress-review-link="true" ts-reviews-url="/reviews"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-8 max-w-2xl lg:content-center lg:order-1">
        <img src="../images/tcg-logo/Blue/TGC_Square_Logo_Blue.svg" alt="The Coders Guild Small Logo" class="w-10 h-7 object-cover">
        <h2 class="mb-0">Empower Your SME with Cutting-Edge Tech Skills</h2>
        <p>Enhance your team’s capabilities with government-funded tech training. Book a free consultation today and discover how our bespoke training plans can upskill your team and boost productivity.</p>
        {% include './includes/components/hub/consultation-button.njk' %}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-[50%] -translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2 flex p-8 items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded shadow-lg max-w-[1000px] mx-auto">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8 flex-1">
        <h2 class="mb-0">Welcome to The Coders Guild</h2>
        <p>In today's fast-paced business environment, staying ahead of the curve is essential. At The Coders Guild, we specialise in transforming your team’s potential through expert-led, government-funded tech training. Whether you're looking to upskill your existing team or onboard new talent, our tailored training plans ensure your business thrives.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Why Upskill -->
  <section class="flex pt-60 px-4 lg:px-48 mx-auto pb-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start gap-10">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:pl-32 items-start gap-8 decorated-list">
        <h2 class="mb-0">Why Upskill Your Team?</h2>
        <p>Investing in your team's development isn't just about new skills—it's about driving your business forward. By accessing government funding, you can:</p>
        <ul class="font-semibold">
          <li>Enhance productivity and efficiency.</li>
          <li>Boost employee morale and retention.</li>
          <li>Increase your team’s billable rate with advanced tech skills.</li>
        </ul>
        {% include './includes/components/hub/consultation-button.njk' %}

      </div>
      <div class="bg-grey-2000 h-full w-full"></div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!--Our Approach -->
  <section class="flex py-8 px-4 lg:px-48 mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start gap-10">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:pl-32 items-start gap-8 decorated-list lg:order-2">
        <h2 class="mb-0">Our Approach to Training</h2>
        <p>At The Coders Guild, we understand that every business is unique. Our bespoke training plans are tailored to align with your specific needs, systems, and tools, ensuring maximum relevance and impact.</p>
        <ul class="font-semibold">
          <li>Customised Learning Journeys: Training programs designed to fit your business processes and technologies.</li>
          <li>Industry-Led Curriculum: Courses crafted by professionals actively working in the field.</li>
          <li>Practical Skills Application: Focused on real-world application and immediate relevance.</li>
        </ul>
        {% include './includes/components/hub/consultation-button.njk' %}
      </div>
      <div class="bg-grey-2000 h-full w-full"></div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Featured Courses and Meet The Trainers -->
  <section class="flex flex-col items-start justify-center py-16 px-4 lg:px-48 gap-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 to-blue-200">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 self-stretch">
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2 text-white text-center">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-white text-center">Featured Courses and Apprenticeships</h2>
        <p class="text-white text-center">Explore our range of training programs designed to meet the evolving needs of the tech industry:</p>
      </div>
      <div id="course-grid-container" data-cards="4">
        {% include './includes/components/global/course-carousel.njk' %}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-12">
      <h2 class="text-white text-center">Meet the Trainers</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:flex-wrap items-start justify-center gap-y-8 self-stretch mx-auto">
        {% for trainer in trainers %}
          <div class="flex flex-col py-0 px-8 justify-center items-center gap-6 lg:w-1/4">
            <img src="{{ trainer.image }}" alt="{{ trainer.name }}'s profile picture" class="w-32 h-32 object-cover rounded-full">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
              <p class="text-white text-center">{{trainer.name}}</p>
              <p class="text-white text-center">{{ trainer.occupation }}</p>
              <div class="flex">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  
  </section>
  
  <!-- testimonial -->
  
  <section class="px-4 lg:px-48">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row py-32 relative gap-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 mt-16 md:w-6/12">
        <h2 class="mb-0">Success Stories</h2>
        <p>See how our training has transformed businesses</p>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-6/12">
        <img class="h-[562px] w-full object-cover rounded shadow" src="../images/testimonials/sam-brand-ambition.jpeg" alt="Sam from Brand Ambition Leeds credits The Coders Guild with transforming his team" />
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-[614px] absolute bottom-0 left-1/12 bg-white overflow-hidden p-100 flex flex-col items-start gap-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        <img class="w-48 h-14 object-cover" src="../images/company-logos/brand-ambition.png" alt="Brand Ambition Logo" />
        <p>"Partnering with The Coders Guild has not only upskilled our team but ingrained a culture of innovation and agility in our operations. Our turnover increased significantly thanks to their funded training programs."</p>
        <p class="text-blue-100 font-bold text-lg">Sam, Brand Ambition</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-1000 to-purple-1000 flex items-start self-stretch gap-4 px-4 lg:px-48 py-32">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center flex-1">
      <div class="w-full max-w-[484px] flex flex-col items-start gap-14 text-white decorated-list white">
        <h2 class="mb-0 text-white font-bold">Book Your Free Consultancy</h2>
        <p class="text-white">Take advantage of our limited-time offer: three free consultancy sessions per week for the next six weeks. <strong>Book a 45-minute session with Crispin Read</strong>, our founder and CEO, to discover how your SME can benefit from government-funded training.</p>
        <ul class="font-bold">
          <li>Get a Personalized Skills Gap Analysis</li>
          <li>Discover Available Funding Opportunities</li>
          <li>Receive a Customized Training Plan</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full max-w-[592px]">
        <!-- Calendly inline widget begin -->
        <div class="calendly-inline-widget" data-url="https://calendly.com/crispin_read/skills-gap-consultancy" style="min-width:320px;height:700px;"></div>
        <script type="text/javascript" src="https://assets.calendly.com/assets/external/widget.js" async></script>
        <!-- Calendly inline widget end --></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {% include './includes/components/hub/faqs.njk' %}
</div>

